						<div class="postbody">Manual Memory management, header and implementation files, having to know the difference between . and -&gt;, c++ is a horror story you tell kids these days. I work with iOS devs, whom struggled with Obj-C and were flat out afraid of C++.I was actually running a &quot;bug ninja&quot; service, where they would hire me to fix their C++ code when they needed to mix it in <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /> Compared to Python, Go,Swift, Ruby, JS, ReactJS, NodeJS whatever the new age mysticism is these days C++ is low level.</div>

